rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, I heard there's a spot
with a great view up ahead.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0002
rows.name: Exciting, isn't it?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0003
rows.name: Oh? I couldn't care less...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't be like that It'll
be fun if we go together!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0005
rows.name:
It doesn't matter how many
people go, it'll be the same.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0006
rows.name: ...I'm going on ahead.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0007
rows.name:
Hey, wait up, Seori!
Don't go by yourself!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0008
rows.name:
...Seori Why are you
being so cold to me?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0009
rows.name:
...I'm like this with
everyone, aren't I?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0010
rows.name: I'm the same way with my Driver too...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0011
rows.name: Well... That's true.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0012
rows.name: Right. Seori has that cool personality.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0013
rows.name:
Yeah, that's right I don't
consider it a bad trait though...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0014
rows.name: Yep. It's very characteristic of Seori.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0015
rows.name:
Umm... That's not what
I'm trying to say...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0016
rows.name: I promised the old Seori

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0017
rows.name: that I would never forget you.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0018
rows.name: She wanted the two of us to stay close.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0019
rows.name: That's why I...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0020
rows.name:
You don't have to care that
much about it, you know?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0021
rows.name: I don't feel that way now...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0022
rows.name:
And both you and I have
lost our memories...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0024
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0025
rows.name: Consider Mikumari's feelings as well.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0026
rows.name: You two are really alike.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0027
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0028
rows.name: Think about Mikumari's feelings too.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0029
rows.name: Y'know, you two are really alike.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0030
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0031
rows.name:
You should think about
Mikumari's feelings too.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0032
rows.name: You two are quite alike.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0033
rows.name: What should I say?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0034
rows.name:
Think about Mikumari's
feelings too, will ya?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0035
rows.name: Y'all are quite alike.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0101
rows.name: I'm sorry...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0102
rows.name: It's not that I want to be cold[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0103
rows.name: No, I get it.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0104
rows.name:
I think to you I'm just one of
many Blades nothing special.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0105
rows.name: Hmm...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0106
rows.name: But I'm different.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0107
rows.name:
I knew the old you and I want
to stay with you forever.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0201
rows.name: Similar[ML:Dash ]?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0202
rows.name:
The previous Mikumari didn't
care much about her memories.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0203
rows.name: So the previous Seori seemed very sad[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0204
rows.name:
Mikumari ndidn't care at all
about her previous memories.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0205
rows.name: So the previous Seori seemed very sad.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0206
rows.name:
Mikumari barely cared about
her previous memories.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0207
rows.name:
So the previous Seori wore
a very sad expression.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0208
rows.name:
The old Mikumari hardly
cared about her memories.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0209
rows.name:
So the previous Seori was
making a super sad face.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0210
rows.name:
So now Mikumari who knows
the previous me is sad?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0211
rows.name:
I'm not that sad yet but if
this keeps up, I might be.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0212
rows.name: Just kidding.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0214
rows.name: You two are like sisters.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0215
rows.name:
It might be odd to call
Blades sisters but...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0216
rows.name: You two are sisters!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0217
rows.name:
It seems odd for Blades to
be sisters but you know.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0218
rows.name: You two are like sisters.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0219
rows.name:
The term sisters might not be
quite right for Blades but...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0220
rows.name: You two are sisters, ain't ya!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0221
rows.name:
It might be weird to call
Blades sisters but...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0222
rows.name: Sisters...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0223
rows.name: "Sisters" sounds nice!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0224
rows.name: Is that alright?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0225
rows.name: Yes! It makes us feel special.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0226
rows.name:
I'll be the older sister and Seori
will be the younger sister!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0227
rows.name: Hmm...

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0228
rows.name:
Seori, would you mind
calling me "Onee-chan"?

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0229
rows.name: No way!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0230
rows.name:
Hmm, I guess it's hard
to start right away.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0231
rows.name:
Well, my dear younger sister,
you can call me "Onee-chan"
any time you want!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0232
rows.name: I will never call you that.

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0233
rows.name: Looks like we've got a long way ahead[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0234
rows.name: But thank you!

rows.label: kizunatalk065_msg0235
rows.name:
I was a little concerned
but now I think I can keep
my promise to Seori!
